snippet.title: Downtown Dealers - Trailer
snippet.description:
Downtown Dealers is an upcoming roguelike deckbuilder with a focus on building cities. 
Wishlist on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1765000/Downtown_Dealers/
Check out the demo during Steam Next Fest from June 19th - 26th
